ng skills, speed, power, precision ... to reach the maximum score and come out victorious.\n\nWelcome a frenetic soccer virtual reality experience to test your best moves and sports skills while being in a breath-taking stadium. \n\nFeatured in the DEMO version:\n - Goalkeeper Mode:  become a goalkeeper and stop as many balls as possible\n - Header Mode: become a striker and head the ball to hit the scoring panels and test your header accuracy.\n\nGet ready for the match!\n\n  Full game coming soon, with:\n     - New Keeper game modes\n     - New Kicker game modes\n     - New Rhythm Fitness mode\n     - More stadiums\n     - More challenges\n     - And more ...", "short_description": "BeFootball - SuperPlayer is a frenetic soccer virtual reality experience to test your best moves and sport skills while being in a breath-taking stadium.\n\nFeatured in the DEMO version:\n - Goalkeeper Mode:  become a goalkeeper and stop as many balls as possible\n - Header Mode: become a striker and head the ball to hit the scoring panels and test your accuracy.\n"}]}, "developer_name": "Prisma VR Studio", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://befootball.world/superplayer-vr-demo-privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://befootball.world/legal-notice", "publisher_name": "BeFootball", "support_website_url": "https://befootball.world/contact", "website_url": "https://befootball.world/superplayer", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "2776542286000603"}, {"id": "331529188132278"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["SPORTS"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes